title: Luc Jobin, CN executive vice-president and chief financial officer, to address two investor conferences in mid-September 2015Travelandtourworld.com
text:
Luc Jobin, CN executive vice-president and chief financial officer, to address two investor conferences in mid-September 2015 Published on : Thursday, September 3, 2015
Luc Jobin , executive vice-president and chief financial officer of CN , will address two investor conferences in mid-September 2015 :
Citi 2015 Industrials Conference, Boston, Mass. , on Sept. 16 starting at 11.45 a.m. Eastern Daylight Time (EDT), and CIBC 14 th Annual Eastern Institutional Investor Conference, Montreal , on Sept. 17 starting at 2.05 p.m. EDT .
Jobin will discuss CN’s continuing focus on supply chain collaboration and Operational and Service Excellence.
CN is a true backbone of the economy, transporting more than C$250 billion worth of goods annually for a wide range of business sectors, ranging from resource products to manufactured products to consumer goods, across a rail network spanning Canada and mid-America. CN – Canadian National Railway Company, along with its operating railway subsidiaries — serves the cities and ports of Vancouver , Prince Rupert, B.C. , Montreal , Halifax , New Orleans , and Mobile, Ala. , and the metropolitan areas of Toronto , Edmonton , Winnipeg , Calgary , Chicago , Memphis , Detroit , Duluth, Minn. / Superior, Wis. , and Jackson, Miss. , with connections to all points in North America .
Source:- CN
